                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Weissman",
                    "No, my lord.{w}{br}We've searched the village, but the prince is nowhere to be found.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Raydrik",
                    "You fool! We don't have much time.{w} I know that the prince is here.{w}{br}Round up the villagers and make them talk!{w}{br}We need to find him!{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Weissman",
                    "Yes, we are already doing that, my lord.{w}{br}But the villagers say that he's not here.{w}{br}He apparently left with the Fiana Freeblades,{w} to go save some village from a pirate attack.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Raydrik",
                    "Fiana Freeblades?{br}What's that?{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Weissman",
                    "This village was originally the headquarters of a large group of brigands.{w}{br}A little over a decade ago, a travelling mercenary named Eyvel{w} cleared out the bandits and took over the village.{w}{br}She then stablished a militia to protect the nearby villages from bandit attacks.{w}{br}Apparently she's quite skilled with her sword...{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Raydrik",
                    "Hmm.... She could be a problem.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Weissman",
                    "No problem, my lord.{br}We've already taken Eyvel's daughter hostage.{w}{br}We've also captured the daugther of Finn, the knight defending the prince.{w}{br}They'll have no choice but to give in to us now.{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Raydrik",
                    "Well, not bad, for you.{w}{br}Good, I shall take girls back to Manster with me.{w}{br}You stay here and wait for the rebels.{w}{br}Make sure to capture the prince when he returns!{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
            [
                "speak",
                [
                    "Weissman",
                    "Yes, my lord{w}",
                    "",
                    "",
                    "noir"
                ]
            ],
